abstract_ssm: Al Viani was the president of the Local in 1964 during the Welfare Department strike of January 1965. This collection is made up primarily of correspondence and press clippings from Viani's days with Local 371, including a scrapbook he kept of the events of January to February 1965.
corpname_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives
